description: Try our easy to follow Haloumi, Prosciutto, Zucchini & Tomato Skewers recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Skewer & kebab,Zucchini,Seafood free,Soy free,Wheat free,Gluten free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Tomato,Sesame free
name: Haloumi, Prosciutto, Zucchini & Tomato Skewers Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 2 tbs extra virgin olive oil (for serving)

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat a chargrill pan over a medium high heat.
Cut halloumi cheese into 12 cubes. Cut prosciutto into 3 short pieces and wrap around halloumi cubes.

Slice zucchini into 3cm thick slices. Thread a prosciutto wrapped cube of halloumi, a cherry tomato and a slice of zucchini onto prepared skewers. Cook skewers on chargrill for 2-3 minutes on each side or until charred.
Transfer to a serving platter. Drizzled with olive oil and sprinkle with freshly ground black pepper before serving.
